WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
A monsoon call comes in at 2am.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:09.000
A puppy is wedged three feet down a storm drain.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:15.000
It takes two hours, and a very narrow harness, to reach her.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Her name, chosen that night, is Kaali.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
People for Animals - the work, made visible.
